<p>It is VERY common and indeed common sense to use different brands of a critical component for security.</p>

<p>This is because the chances are the the same brand component is likely to have the same point of failure. Therefor two different brands are used as they are unlikely to have the same point of failure. In aerospace systems this is the MINIMUM requirement i.e. several IMUs all of different brands.</p>
